description: Under normal market conditions, the Adviser seeks to achieve the fund’s investment objective by investing at least 80% of the UST 12 Month Bill Fund’s net assets (plus any borrowings for investment purposes) in the component securities of the index. The underlying index is comprised of a single issue purchased at the beginning of the month and held for a full month.
name: The RBB Fund, Inc. - US Treasury 12 Month Bill ETF
